d:
Iriska is an experienced witch and alchemist who is forced to live and hide in a city where witchcraft is forbidden. But at some point she encounters dark and mysterious forces that force her to plunge into the abyss, where something demonic is waiting for her, capable of changing her being and forever forgetting the way back.
